I"º<p>Deception Royale is a <strong>2D top-down multiplayer battle royale</strong> game, where each player tries to remain the last one standing. Up to 20 people can connect to a match and play against each other. The game was made as an entry to the <a href="https://itch.io/jam/2nd-winter-game-jam">2nd AAU Winter Game Jam</a>.
