<p>The game was built using the <strong>Unity3D</strong> engine and written in <strong>C#</strong>. I worked in a <strong>team of two</strong> on this, as a <strong>gameplay programme</strong>r. A mini-map functionality was also added programmed by me. For the multiplayer, we used Unity‚Äôs <strong>UNet API</strong>.</p>

